    "Furthermore, AU-TOACT tends to consume more planning rounds than other methods (the specific average planning rounds is in Appx.",
    "This allows AUTOACT to perform better on harder problems.",
    "However, this characteristic can be a double-edged sword when it comes to simple problems.",
